  -gb_list <arg>             file containing list of modules to be glassboxed
  -gcc_vers <vers>           9.3 or 6.3 Linux only
  -gdb                       Run xmsim under gdb
  -gdbelab                   Run xmelab under gdb
  -gdbhref                   Run genhref under gdb
