  -gdbsh                     Force gdb to run under sh instead of user SHELL
  -gdbvlog                   Run xmvlog under gdb
  -genafile <file>           Generate an access file for PLI/TCL
  -genassert_synth_pragma    Enable generating assertions from synth pragma
